Innocent Asonze (amuru Disemba 13, 1972) bu onye oso si Naijiria

Ya na Francis Obikwelu, Daniel Effiong na Deji Aliu o nwetara ihe nrite ọla nchara na 4 x 100 mita n'asọmpi  egwuregwu ụwa nke 1999, mana e mechapụrụ ndị otu ahụ (na August 2005) n'ihi na ọ dara ule doping na June 1999
Àtụ:Footer All-Africa Champions 4 × 100 m relay Men
